<div class="sm-page-template">

  <section class="sm-section sm-bg-light-green">
    <div class="sm-container sm-flex sm-align-center">
      <div class="sm-col-50 sm-hero-text">
        <h1>How SmartMouth™ Works</h1>
        <p>SmartMouth™’s patented formula combines a sulfur eliminating liquid with a zinc ion activating liquid that are kept separate until you pour. SmartMouth™’s activated rinses eliminate bad breath instantly and prevent sulfur gas from returning for 24 hours with just two rinses a day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sm-col-50">
        <div class="sm-video-wrapper">
          <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/U_MK_PQkT0M?autoplay=1&mute=1&playsinline=1&loop=1&rel=0&controls=0&playlist=U_MK_PQkT0M" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sm-section sm-bg-white">
    <div class="sm-container sm-text-center">
      <h2 class="sm-section-title">All day bad breath prevention with Smart-Zinc™ Technology</h2>
      <img class="sm-main-banner" src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/How-it-works-v1-1-scaled.jpg" alt="How it works">
      
      <div class="sm-flex sm-align-start sm-mt-40">
        <div class="sm-col-50 sm-px-20">
          <img class="sm-icon-img" src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/germs-protein-e1743492343110.png" alt="Germs + Protein">
          <h3 class="sm-col-title">Germs + Protein in Our Saliva = Sulfur Gas, AKA The Real Cause of Bad Breath</h3>
          <p>When poured in the cup, SmartMouth™’s two liquids — the Sulfur Eliminating Solution, which destroys sulfur gases, and the zinc ion Activating Solution, activate to release billions of zinc ions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm-col-50 sm-px-20">
          <img class="sm-icon-img" src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/germs-zinc.png" alt="Germs + Zinc">
          <h3 class="sm-col-title">Germs + SmartMouth™ Activated Zinc Ion Solution = No More Bad Breath</h3>
          <p>It’s this zinc ion activation technology that blocks germs from consuming protein particles inside your mouth. This is the key to preventing sulfur gas production and the secret to all day bad breath prevention.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sm-video-wrapper sm-mt-40" style="max-width: 900px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lBex50BHOSY?rel=0&showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sm-section sm-bg-blue">
    <div class="sm-container">
      <div class="sm-grid-3">
        <div class="sm-feature-card">
          <img src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Dual-Chamber-Bottle.png" alt="Dual Chamber">
          <h3>Dual Chamber Bottle</h3>
          <p>The original SmartMouth™ dual chamber bottle is scientifically designed to harness the power of both bad breath fighting solutions, leaving the power of zinc ion activation in your hands every time you pour.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm-feature-card">
          <img src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Zinc-Rich-Activator.png" alt="Zinc Rich">
          <h3>Zinc Rich Activator</h3>
          <p>The Zinc Rich Solution activates when you pour, releasing billions of zinc ions that bond to the germs in your mouth, preventing bad breath for 12 hours with every rinse.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm-feature-card">
          <img src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Sulfur-Eliminator.png" alt="Sulfur Eliminator">
          <h3>Sulfur Eliminator</h3>
          <p>The Sulfur Eliminating Solution destroys any existing bad breath gases in your mouth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm-feature-card">
          <img src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Safe-for-Kids-Diabetics.png" alt="Safe for Kids">
          <h3>Safe for People with Diabetes and Kids</h3>
          <p>100% paraben-free zinc ion oral rinse.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm-feature-card">
          <img src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Clinical-Strength.png" alt="Clinical Strength">
          <h3>Clinical Strength</h3>
          <p>An alcohol-free, anti-plaque and anti-gingivitis solution.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm-feature-card">
          <img src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Powerful-Feel-Taste.png" alt="Powerful Feel">
          <h3>Powerful Feel and Great Taste</h3>
          <p>It’s a new kind of feel, a smart kind of clean.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sm-section sm-bg-white">
    <div class="sm-container">
      <div class="sm-text-center sm-mb-40">
        <h2 class="sm-section-title">What’s Your Reason to Pour?</h2>
        <p style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">Many factors contribute to bad breath, but SmartMouth™’s zinc ion technology provides THE solution to stop bad breath at the source and prevent it from coming back for 24 hours. Learn how below!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="sm-flex sm-align-center sm-row-alternate">
        <div class="sm-col-50">
          <img src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/causes.jpg" alt="Causes of Bad Breath" class="sm-responsive-img">
        </div>
        <div class="sm-col-50 sm-px-40">
          <h2>Causes of Bad Breath</h2>
          <p>Everyone experiences bad breath because it’s a naturally occurring process. Our mouths can contain billions of germs, and these bacteria break down protein particles in our saliva or near our gum line. When they do, they produce foul-smelling sulfur gas, otherwise known as bad breath.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sm-flex sm-align-center sm-row-alternate sm-reverse-mobile">
        <div class="sm-col-50 sm-px-40">
          <h2>You Activate the Zinc Ions</h2>
          <p>When the two solutions come together, a chemical reaction occurs that instantly releases billions of zinc ions.</p>
          <p>When you first pour the rinse, you’ll notice it’s green. That means the solution is freshly activated and the zinc ions are ready to bind to germs.</p>
          <p>But, if you wait 5 minutes after pouring, you’ll notice the poured mouthwash turns blue. That means the zinc ions are no longer as effective at preventing bad breath.</p>
          <p>So remember, always use SmartMouth™ immediately after pouring!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm-col-50">
          <img src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ZincTech-1030x852.jpg" alt="Zinc Activation" class="sm-responsive-img">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sm-flex sm-align-center sm-row-alternate">
        <div class="sm-col-50">
          <img src="https://www.smartmouth.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/24Hours-1030x852.jpg" alt="24 Hour Protection" class="sm-responsive-img">
        </div>
        <div class="sm-col-50 sm-px-40">
          <h2>Two Rinses a Day Keeps Bad Breath Away</h2>
          <p>SmartMouth™ Mouthwash doesn’t mask bad breath. It stops it at the source.</p>
          <p>Preventative care is the key to overcoming the problem of bad breath, and SmartMouth™ is the way to achieve real, lasting results.</p>
          <p>Just two rinses a day will put your worries about embarrassing bad breath to rest and allow you to feel confident about getting up close.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sm-section sm-bg-light-green">
    <div class="sm-container">
      <h2 class="sm-section-title sm-text-center">Our Best-Selling Products</h2>
      <div class="sm-grid-3 sm-mt-40">
        {% for product in collections['frontpage'].products limit: 3 %}
          <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="sm-product-card">
            <img src="{{ product.featured_image | img_url: '600x' }}" alt="{{ product.title | escape }}">
            <h3>{{ product.title }}</h3>
            <div class="sm-price">
              {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
                <span class="sm-compare-price">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
              {% endif %}
              <span class="sm-current-price">{{ product.price | money }}</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        {% else %}
          <div class="sm-text-center" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">Please assign products to your "frontpage" collection to see them here.</div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sm-section sm-bg-light-grey">
    <div class="sm-container">
      <h2 class="sm-section-title sm-text-center">What People Are Saying About SmartMouth™</h2>
